		{
			dependencies: ["7D3CA5C984F11D23"]
			description: [
				"Have you boiled water before? No? Well, I'm going to show you how."
				""
				"You must place the crucible above a source of heat, such as fire. Then, fill the crucible with water and let it boil."
				""
				"Crucibles are unique because their recipes have multiple steps, like real-life recipes. Also similarly to real life, you must execute the steps in order."
				""
				"Sometimes, the pestle must be used to stir the ingredients, which can be done by right-clicking the crucible with an empty hand. This is indicated by a slash in the recipe shown in JEI."
				""
				"When you insert the ingredients for one step, it will make a sound to indicate when ready for the insertion of new items."
				""
				"*If you drop items in bulk into a crucible, it will not try to make multiple batches of the output!!!"
			]
			id: "7017FB66F6F3B2DE"
			rewards: [
				{
