		{
			dependencies: ["441A75FB80582637"]
			description: [
				"You will need a means of communicating with the dark powers. Though rudimentary, the simple wood-straw combination works fine."
				""
				"Place the straw effigy atop the wooden altar."
				""
				"When done, when close to the altar, click on your sign's portrait in your Ars Ecclesia to add it as a component of your chant. This menu can be foudn under the tab with the pentacle icon. "
				""
				"When your book looks like the image below, click the green button."
				""
				"{image:kubejs:item/chant_selection width:707 height:418 align:center fit:true}"
				""
				"If you did it right, thunder will be heard and the effigy's eyes will light up. You'll also see a progress meter at the top of your screen."
				""
				"Continue doing this ritual until the Dark Lord gives you knowledge of a new one. Note that only 1 ritual can be effective per in-game day."
				""
				"optional: Eidolon's Candles can enhance your altar."
			]
			id: "0D59972E42B4D7A5"
			rewards: [{
