		{
			dependencies: ["0D59972E42B4D7A5"]
			description: [
				"Eventually, you'll learn the Blood Sign. First, craft a Goblet. This one is different in that it demands a blood sacrifice. Kill a sheep near the altar and watch the goblet fill with blood. Then, you're good to use your new chant."
				""
				"The composition of this chant should be Wicked --> Blood --> Wicked, as shown below. Make sure the goblet has blood before you use the chant, and the effigy is still somewhere near the altar."
