		{
			dependencies: ["40A4602377E4E3F2"]
			description: [
				"Starbuncles are elusive rodents found in forests who aren't so fond of players, but love golden nuggets. They will not flee if you're holding one while approaching."
				""
				"Give your golden nugget to the Starbuncle and it will turn into a charm. You can use the Charm on the ground to summon the Starbuncle."
				""
				"{@pagebreak}"
				"The Starbuncle, like the hoarder it is, will pick up items from the ground and can move items across storage containers. Right click the Starbuncle with the Dominion Wand and then right click the container to tell it to place items into it."
				""
				"To take from the container, interact with the container and then the Starbuncle."
				""
				"You can get much more precise with these little critters. Refer to your Worn Notebook for more."
			]
			id: "421227890C2EBBA4"
			rewards: [{
				count: 12
				id: "00BD61F29EA8F519"
				item: "lightmanscurrency:coin_iron"
				type: "item"
			}]
			subtitle: "My precious!"
