					tag: { }
				}
				type: "item"
			}]
			x: 15.5d
			y: -3.0d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["2A2B25F44A4AE27B"]
			description: [
				"Have you ever said: \"I want a break from all these magic mods which are really just Thinly Veiled Tech Mods!\""
				""
				"Well, you're in for a treat."
				""
				"Iron's Spellbooks is nothing but spellcasting and adventure. It's the closest thing in the modpack to playing a &5Wizard in DnD&r (just replace Spell Slots with a mana bar). You'll see what I mean in due time."
				""
				"&l&dFirst&r,&r you'll want to find a &dScroll.&r These are single use spells, so it's best to save them for emergencies or wait until you can subscribe them to use as much as you'd like."
				""
				"&dScrolls&r can be found by adventuring or made using a &5Scroll Forge&r later."
			]
			id: "1FAF889506FFFF18"
			rewards: [{
				count: 8
				id: "1DC8C739BE2E37D7"
				item: "lightmanscurrency:coin_iron"
