		{
			dependencies: ["27DF7D39245E5ACB"]
			description: [
				"An &dinscription table&r is commonly found in &5villages&r and many &5towers&r you can come across in your world. You could also craft one yourself, it isn't that hard. &5Complete the task by looking at a table.&r"
				""
				"Using the &dinscription table&r, you can copy &5spells&r from &5scrolls&r into a &dspell book&r. This lets you cast them as many times as you want, within limitations of cooldowns and mana of course."
				""
				"&o&7Note: equip the spell book as a curio to cast spells from it. If the spell book is in the inscription table and you leave the GUI, it will automatically move to your spell book curio slot for convenience."
