		{
			dependencies: ["5390B26927C70B16"]
			description: [
				"Some of these can be more powerful than what you have access to at the point in the game where they're accessible, so it might be worth finding and using these books."
				""
				"Here's how to get each one, since they're not all straightforward:"
				""
				"&9Guide to Watery Whispers&r: find an aquamancer's tower on the beach and take the book on the lectern at the top. Be sure to take care of the aquamancer, since she won't be happy to see you. Then, find an aqua grandmaster wandering a beach, talk to her at night, and trade for this spell book."
				""
				"&dShellbound&r: dropped by amethyst crabs."
				""
				"&cGrimoire of Evocation&r: dropped rarely by evokers or archevokers."
				""
				"&2Rotten Spell Book&r: rarely found while exploring the world."
				""
				"&6Blaze Instruction Manual&r: dropped rarely by blazes."
				""
				"&aVillager Bible&r: in the evoker fort, there's a lectern with a book on it. Take it and give it to a captive wandering trader in the structure to have them translate it. Then, trade the translated book to a village priest."
			]
