		{
			dependencies: ["710393BF8AD587A8"]
			description: [
				"Let's get started with some more logical magic: Theurgy. I'm sure the hardcore alchemists would put my head on a pike for categorizing it as \"supernatural magic,\" but I've no other choice for the sake of organization."
				""
				"We're going to use some carefully calculated actions to convert one raw ore into three raw ingots."
				""
				"Start by crafting and placing all the blocks you need to complete this quest. It doesn't make a difference where, except the sal ammoniac accumulator needs to be on top of the tank."
				"{@pagebreak}"
				"Wait, what do all these unfamiliar blocks do? Let me briefly explain:"
				""
				"- Pyromantic Brazier: generates power by burning fuels"
				"- Calcination Oven: creates mineral salt"
				"- Sal Ammoniac Accumulator: fills the tank with sal ammoniac"
				"- Sal Ammoniac Tank: stores the Sal Ammoniac for the cauldron"
				"- Liquefaction Cauldron: extracts Alchemical Sulfur from sal ammoniac"
				""
				"Once you're done setting up and putting something like coal on the braziers, it's time to move on to the next quest."
			]
			id: "7D0E6CC8E50E7DC5"
			rewards: [{
				count: 10
				id: "411323C031F58F20"
				item: "lightmanscurrency:coin_iron"
