		{
			dependencies: ["2878EB75598EB9F3"]
			description: [
				"The Thought-Knot allows for storing iotas without the Stack."
				""
				"To store an iota, hold the Thought-Knot in your off-hand and use Scribe's Gambit to remove the top iota and store it in the Thought-Knot."
				""
				"When you need the iota again, cast Scribe's Reflection to push the data in the Thought-Knot to the Stack."
				""
				"Once data is read to the Thought-Knot, it can be written to the stack multiple times but cannot be erased or overwritten. As such, it's best to craft multiple if planning on using these innovations."
			]
			id: "374CF15A2D92A76F"
			rewards: [{
				count: 5
				id: "19DBEE7812847EE6"
				item: "lightmanscurrency:coin_iron"
