		}
		{
			dependencies: ["2878EB75598EB9F3"]
			description: [
				"Functionally, Foci are Thought-Knots but reusable. Casting Scribe's Gambit will write over whatever's in the Focus with the top iota."
				""
				"Reading from the Focus is identical to the Thought-Knot; just use Scribe's Reflection."
				""
				"To ensure your Focus is not overwritten, craft it with a Honeycomb. This process is reversibe by casting Erase Item."
