		{
			dependencies: ["77D2B63352A1CDD6"]
			description: [
				"You'll need to supply one of the target sulfur and at least one of the source sulfur. You should plan to bring multiple sources for convenience, though."
				""
				"Make sure the target and source are the same tier (use JEI/EMI for this). You can't just convert rotten flesh into netherite, even though it'd be cool if you could. An example of a valid conversion is emerald to diamond."
				""
				"Put your source and target into the right pedestal, when wait. If you've done everything right up to this point, a glowing orb will appear over the pedestals."
				""
				"Remember to power your array using a Mercury Catalyst. The ritual should start automatically."
				"{@pagebreak}"
				"Once you're done, an orb will appear over the Result Pedestal, which you can take a copy of the target from."
				""
				"You'll notice the target is still there, but the source disappeared. You've now duplicated a material - well done!"
			]
			id: "247ACED8E76DD567"
			rewards: [{
				count: 6
				id: "6D88A7922900456A"
				item: "lightmanscurrency:coin_iron"
				type: "item"
			}]
			subtitle: "&7This quest completes easily, but make sure to read the description"
