			dependencies: ["2626C487E7BA6230"]
			description: [
				"The Storage Lectern is an advanced storage option that uses Bookwyrms! "
				""
				"It works like an Inventory Connector, where external inventories can be connected to the Lectern. To link an inventory, use a Bookwyrm Charm on it. Then, configure access using a Dominion Wand. Any inventory can be linked as long as it's at most 30 blocks away."
				""
				"You can also connect multiple lecterns to each other. In this case, one lectern still serves the role of the root, while another acts as an access point which can extract and insert but not connect directly to inventories."
