				"If you would rather have cute little workers running around your factory instead of boring pipes, these are your items!"
				""
				"The StarbAttery lets a Starbuncle carry energy from your batteries or generators to other machines."
				""
				"The Wyrm Degree lets a Starbuncle input/output items, but only from a specific face of a container. Use Direction Scrolls to configure this."
