		{
			dependencies: ["1FAF889506FFFF18"]
			description: [
				"For each magic school, there is a charm that you can spend around 12 levels to imbue with a random spell from that school."
				""
				"All of these charms can be found in chests, and they give a decent boost to all spells of that school, not just the imbued one!"
				""
				"If you don't like the spell you got or aren't interested in the school, you can smelt echoes into resonant scrap, which you can craft new echoes with and other things too."
