		{
			dependencies: ["2A2B25F44A4AE27B"]
			description: [
				"Somewhere between light and dark lie the spirit arcana, which focus on reading (and harvesting) the souls of living creatures."
				""
				"To start, you'll want to head underground and find yourself some soulstone. This is a special sort of rock with the special ability to harbor souls."
				""
				"Your main use for soulstones at this moment is to incorporate it into a Crude Scythe, which will glean the souls from living creatures killed with it."
				""
				"&7Malum was recently added to the modpack and I haven't finished these quests yet. For more information, see the Encyclopedia Arcana, included in your Eccentric Tome."
