		{
			dependencies: ["304860DD2E9FA817"]
			description: [
				"By placing Runewood Logs above a Runewood Totem Base, you create a pole which can be infused with spirit to provide boons for the surrounding area, similar to a beacon."
				""
				"Embed spirit into a pole by right clicking the logs with spirit in hand. When you're done, right click the base to initiate the ritual."
				""
				" To remove spirits from a totem pole, right click them with an axe as if you were about to strip the log."
				""
				"The Totemic Staff is useful for seeing the area affected by a Totem."
				""
				"This is one of those times when I tell you to grab an Eccentric Tome, look inside the Encyclopedia Arcana, and pan the graph up to where the rituals are and see what you need. In a future update, I will include descriptions on them all here."
			]
